      <h1>Ikigai and Career Fulfillment: Finding Work That Feels Worth Doing</h1>
      <p class="article-subtitle">Ikigai — the Japanese concept of a reason for being — offers a four-part framework for finding work that is meaningful, skilled, needed, and sustainable. Here is how to apply it practically.</p>
      <span>By <strong>{author}</strong></span>
    </header>

